column2: SELECT   A.UIIID,A.RAJ2#WISE_AGN_R9#_ptsrc_VIZIER,A.DEJ2#WISE_AGN_R9#_ptsrc_VIZIER,          B.z,B.zerr,B.class,B.subClass,B.specObjID,C.specObjID as specObjIDClean,B.ObjID FROM   MyDB.CasjobsCombinedOutputBrief AS A, SpecPhotoAll AS B   LEFT JOIN SpecObj as C ON B.specObjID=C.specObjID WHERE   A.petroMag_uSDSSDR1#!=&&&   AND B.class!=&&&   AND ABS(A.petroMag_uSDSSDR1#-B.petroMag_u)<=#   AND ABS(A.petroMag_gSDSSDR1#-B.petroMag_g)<=#   AND ABS(A.petroMag_rSDSSDR1#-B.petroMag_r)<=#   AND ABS(A.petroMag_iSDSSDR1#-B.petroMag_i)<=#   AND ABS(A.petroMag_zSDSSDR1#-B.petroMag_z)<=#   AND A.UIIID BETWEEN # AND # GROUP BY     A.UIIID INTO    MyDB.CasjobsCombinedOutputBrief_SpecPhotoAll_MagSpace
